title: Exception thrown when exporting data in table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when exporting data in the table inside the grid cell.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data in the table inside the grid cell.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data in one of the tables.
